    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It\u2019s been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
