    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks, further protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather is supple and free of any wear on the bolsters, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively at certified dealerships. The engine bay is pristine, and the high-performance tires have excellent tread depth remaining. This is not just a used car; it is a museum-quality investment for a buyer who demands perfection. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
